name: Farmer's Walk
description: Brace your core. Walk with weights in each hand at your sides.

name: Warm-up
description: Warm up your body using any combination of cardio exercises.

name: Cool-down
description: Cool down your body by doing some light cardio exercises.

name: Jumping Jacks
description: Alternate jumping your legs wide to narrow and arms wide then back to your side.

name: Mountain Climbers
description: Alternate bringing your knees close to your chin while in plank position.

name: High Knees
description: Alternate bringing your knees up quickly while standing.

name: Burpees
description: Starting from plank, do a push-up, jump your legs forward, then jump with high knees, and return to plank position.

name: High Arms Alternating Knees
description: With arms in the air, alternate one knee up to your waist as you crunch down with your arms.

name: Treadmill
description: Walking, jogging, running, or sprints.

name: Elliptical
description: Standard elliptical machine.

name: Stair Stepper
description: Standard stair stepper machine.

name: Straight Lunges
description: Standing or walking straight lunges.

name: Side Lunges
description: Standing alternating side lunges.

name: Stretching
description: Spend a few minutes stretching muscles you have or plan to use.

name: Bench Press
description: Brace your core and keep your butt on the bench. Push weight above chest.

name: Chest Press
description: Push weight above chest.

name: Incline Bench Press
description: Brace your core. Push weight above chest while at an incline.

name: Incline Chest Press
description: Push weight above chest while at an incline.

name: Decline Bench Press
description: Brace your core. Push weight above chest while at a decline.

name: Decline Chest Press
description: Push weight above chest while at a decline.

name: Diamond Push-ups
description: Place hands next to eachother under chest while in plank position and push up.

name: Military Push-ups
description: Place hands under shoulders while in plank position and push up keeping the elbows next to your body.

name: Standard Push-ups
description: Place hands slightly outside of shoulders while in plank position and push up.

name: Wide Push-ups
description: Place hands wide outside of shoulders while in plank position and push up.

name: Pike Push-ups
description: Push up and down with the arms while in downward dog position.

name: Chest Side Pulls
description: Stand and pull weight to stomach while keeping elbow locked to your side.

name: Overhead Press
description: Stand up straight, brace your core and lower back. Press weight above head.

name: Side Arm Raises
description: Raise straight arms up from the sides of your body.

name: Front Arm Raises
description: Raise straight arms up in front of your body.

name: Shrugs
description: Brace your core. Lift with your shoulders while standing with arms extended.

name: Tricep Kickbacks
description: Bend at waist while standing and extend arms backward.

name: Tricep Pulldowns
description: Pull cables directly down and hold briefly while standing.

name: Tricep Overhead Extentions
description: Face away from cable machine and pull weight overhead.

name: Laying Tricep Extension
description: Hold weight above head while laying down and bend elbows to lower weight behind head.

name: Dips
description: Hold body up by arms on an elavated surface and lower yourself down and back up.

name: Bent Over Back Flyes
description: Lean over with arms hanging down and pull arms up and slightly wider while bringing your shoulder blades together.

name: Bent Over Rows
description: Bend over with chest above weight and arms fully extended. Brace your core and lower back. Pull weight up to bottom of ribcage.

name: Stiff Leg Deadlift
description: Brace your core and lower back. Stand slightly away from weight and lift with your back while keeping your legs nearly straight.

name: Deadlift
description: Brace your core and lower back. Stand slightly away from weight and lift while keeping your knees behind your toes.

name: Standard Pull-ups
description: Shoulder width overhand grip. Get your chin above the bar.

name: Wide Overhand Pull-ups
description: Wide overhand grip. Get your chin above the bar.

name: Chin-ups
description: Close underhand grip. Get your chin above the bar.

name: Hammer Grip Pull-ups
description: Close hammer grip. Get your chin above the bar.

name: Face Pulls
description: Pull directly towards your face.

name: T-Rows
description: Brace your core. Grip center of barbell and lift in front of you with your arms and elbows higher than it. Bring the barbell up to your neck.

name: Overhand Bicep Curls
description: Bicep curl with overhand grip.

name: Underhand Bicep Curls
description: Standard bicep curl.

name: Hammer Bicep Curls
description: Bicep curl with hammer grip.

name: Squats
description: Brace your core. Hold barbell weight on your upper back. Hold free weights where comfortable. Squat down until your thighs are about parallel with the ground and stand up straight again.

name: Leg Curls
description: Lay stomach down on bench and curl legs up.

name: Leg Extensions
description: Lay back down on bench and extend legs out.

name: Calf Raises
description: Hold the weight and pull as you lift onto the balls of your feet and back down again.

name: Calf Raises
description: Hold a weight at your side or on your shoudler and lift onto the balls of your feet and back down again.

name: Hip Thrusters
description: Brace your core. Prop your upper back on a bench while holding the weight at your waist. Thrust upward to tabletop position.

name: Plank
description: Standard plank position.

name: Oblique Side Bends
description: Hold weight at your side with arms extended. Lean down and back up with the weight.

name: Abdominal Crunch
description: Crunch while laying down with or without weight.

name: Alternating Torso Twist
description: Hold cable handle with both hands and twist away from machine like you are swinging a baseball bat.

name: Russian Twist
description: Sit with feet off the ground while you twist and tap the ground on each side of you.
